Subject:[bcp] Ride Cancelled
A ride has been cancelled.  This is a description of the ride: 

Wed November 7, 2012 - CANCELLED  Mort Packel memorial Wednesday morning breakfast ride  meet at Lloyd Hall at the start of boat house row behind the art museium @ 10:00 am Class C-, 12mph, 20 miles, The late Mort Packel led a group of mostly retired riders every Wednesday morning on a fun, informal ride. I'd like to bring that back. Bring a lock ;and money for lunch and enjoy inspired conversation and good companionship. Alternate ride suggestions are very welcome. Bring lock and money for a light meal. Ride automatically canceled because of rain, temperatures below freezing, and slippery streets
 
 Leaders:  mailto:hlazar@verizon.net - Henry L.  Lazarus - phone: 267-259-6275    Check the ride calendar if you want more information about this ride.

